commit.message: Added more configuration to the amazon_worker and cleaned up more debugging code.
Added a cors middleware to the server and cleaned up the amazon_worker.
Added support for pulling the author and title from a amazon listing.
Fixed the amazon_worker to ignore sponsored postings to increase result quality.
Updated imports and started writing API call
Updated the workers to be more complete and changed the amazon_worker to use a method from document_utils to filter out ads (still wip).
Added an entity to represent book listings.
Added the basic version of the Amazon listing scraping.
Added a gitignore to the server project.

Added ISBN verifictation and an alert message.

UNL Bookstore Worker was also added
Added code to display results and seller logos
